# The Dwarf "vendor" for constants Reference

<DoxygenPage pluginConfig={pluginConfig}>

These functions return an identifier describing &quot;who&quot; defined the constant, either the DWARF standard itself or the vendor who defined the extension. <a href="#details">More...</a>

## Description {#details}

These functions return an identifier describing &quot;who&quot; defined the constant, either the DWARF standard itself or the vendor who defined the extension.
